  "title": "Strategic Partnerships Manager (SME Financing Solutions)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Design and implement <strong>channel and partnership strategies </strong>to broaden market reach and accelerate revenue growth.</li><li>Identify, negotiate, and manage strategic alliances with distributors, referral partners, and intermediaries.</li><li>Evaluate market trends and channel performance to uncover growth opportunities and strengthen existing partnerships.</li><li>Work closely with Sales, Marketing, and Product teams to ensure partnership initiatives align with overall business objectives.</li><li>Monitor, analyze, and report on channel and partner performance, providing actionable insights for continuous improvement.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Business, Marketing, or equivalent</li><li>At least 4 years of hands-on experience managing <strong>channel partnerships </strong>within SME financing, including <strong>working capital and small business funding solutions.</strong></li><li>Strong negotiation, relationship management, and data-driven decision-making capabilities.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br />Registration: R1326740</p>",
